I"Õ<p>The <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">FAMILY</code> relation is annotated between two <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">PERSON</code> entities that
are stated to stand in any familial relationship.</p>

<!-- details -->

<p>Example:</p>

<pre><code class="language-ann">Michelle Obama is the wife of Barack Obama.
T1 PERSON 0 14 Michelle Obama
T2 PERSON 30 42 Barack Obama
R1 FAMILY Arg1:T1 Arg2:T2
</code></pre>

